To install this sample Chrome Web App:

1) Download the files into an App folder in your web server directory
2) In Chrome go to chrome://flags and enable on the Experimental Extension APIs
3) Restart your browser
4) Go to chrome://extensions, expand Developer Mode in the upper right and use pack extension button to pack the directory to which you downloaded your app files
5) Clear your browsing data to make sure you have the latest version
6) Point your browser to the .crx file created by the packing process and install the app
7) Open a new tab and you will see the app.